I also ordered a coconut mint mojito but requested they leave out the soda water, which then left me with a drink half the size the norm. Which I understand, less ingredients, smaller glass but I was also unaware I was paying almost $10 for soda water.  I would suggest others come here for a quiet brunch or just grab a beer with all the craziness of the beach or bar type environment.
